        <time datetime="2026-06-14">June 14, 2026</time><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><span>9 min read</span><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔤</span> Word Finder</a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">The history of competitive Scrabble is punctuated by extraordinary moments — games that defied probability, players who achieved the seemingly impossible, and matches that kept audiences breathless. These famous encounters showcase the game at its most dramatic, where preparation meets opportunity and legends are born from a bag of 100 tiles.</p>

