          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Vocabulary wins championships:</span> Every record game required word knowledge that casual players simply do not have. The investment in study directly enables the spectacular plays that make headlines.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Board position enables records:</span> High-scoring plays need premium square access. Players who maintain open boards and create opportunities for big plays set themselves up for potential record moments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Composure under pressure:</span> Championship finals are won by players who maintain clarity when everything is on the line. Mental preparation is as important as word study for peak performance moments.</p>
        </div>
